59
00:04:11,620 --> 00:04:13,160
in Coach Li's abilities?

60
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:15,280
Dad.

61
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:16,360
No.

62
00:04:16,940 --> 00:04:18,080
Coach Li,

63
00:04:18,690 --> 00:04:20,970
