64
00:04:20,970 --> 00:04:22,680
Now, I officially welcome you

65
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,760
to join our beach volleyball team.

66
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:25,280
No, Duoduo,

67
00:04:25,780 --> 00:04:26,720
