431
00:20:49,820 --> 00:20:50,740
How is it?

432
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:53,380
Did you draw me?

433
00:20:53,380 --> 00:20:54,340
Of course, it's you.

434
00:20:54,340 --> 00:20:55,300
Who else would it be?

435
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:55,940
It's nice, right?

436
00:20:57,940 --> 00:20:59,460
Nice?

437
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:00,460
You didn't even capture

438
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:01,740
a tenth of my beauty.

439
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:02,900
I even enhanced

440
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:04,260
your features a bit,

441
00:21:04,260 --> 00:21:05,380
and I drew your hair.

442
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:06,980
Am I bald?

443
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:09,060
- No, no, not bald.
- Stop joking.

444
00:21:09,060 --> 00:21:10,420
Forget the hair for now.

445
00:21:11,860 --> 00:21:12,780
Duoduo,

446
00:21:13,220 --> 00:21:13,980
look.

447
00:21:14,220 --> 00:21:15,300
When spiking,

448
00:21:15,620 --> 00:21:16,620
your elbow

449
00:21:17,020 --> 00:21:18,740
should be slightly above your shoulder.

450
00:21:19,700 --> 00:21:20,980
The elbow, shoulder, and waist

451
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:22,340
should form a line

452
00:21:22,580 --> 00:21:24,220
at about a 135-degree angle.

453
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:25,060
See?

454
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:27,700
Your elbow is too low, right?

455
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:28,940
This affects your power.

456
00:21:31,300 --> 00:21:32,620
It's a lack of training

457
00:21:32,980 --> 00:21:34,060
and coaching.

458
00:21:38,820 --> 00:21:40,860
Uncle Li, you're impressive.

459
00:21:40,860 --> 00:21:41,940
You can tell so much

460
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:43,060
from just a picture.

461
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:45,380
Then I should...

462
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:05,420
You like this picture so much

463
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:06,540
that you hang it over your bed?

464
00:22:07,780 --> 00:22:09,740
I just want to practice

465
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:12,020
my spiking form before bed.

466
00:22:12,820 --> 00:22:14,580
Alright, your dedication is admirable.

467
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:15,820
Of course.

468
00:22:15,820 --> 00:22:17,260
Beach volleyball is my dream.

469
00:22:17,980 --> 00:22:18,860
Dream, huh?

470
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:20,940
No wonder you want to practice before bed.

471
00:22:20,940 --> 00:22:22,220
You want to dream about it.

472
00:22:23,020 --> 00:22:24,140
Are you mocking me?

473
00:22:24,460 --> 00:22:25,340
Not at all.

474
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:26,540
I really respect

475
00:22:26,540 --> 00:22:27,980
people like you

476
00:22:27,980 --> 00:22:28,900
who pursue their dreams.

477
00:22:28,900 --> 00:22:29,740
That's right.

478
00:22:29,740 --> 00:22:30,740
People who chase their dreams

479
00:22:30,740 --> 00:22:31,860
shine brightly.

480
00:22:32,340 --> 00:22:33,860
Look at me.

481
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:34,860
Am I shining now?

482
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:36,700
Sorry.

483
00:22:36,700 --> 00:22:37,580
I have a bit of astigmatism.

484
00:22:37,580 --> 00:22:38,740
I can't see your glow.

485
00:22:39,940 --> 00:22:41,180
Hey, bring me a hammer

486
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:42,140
and two nails.

487
00:22:42,380 --> 00:22:43,020
Okay.

488
00:22:44,540 --> 00:22:46,100
- Is this the one?
- It'll do.

489
00:22:46,940 --> 00:22:47,820
How about

490
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:48,620
putting it here?

491
00:22:49,100 --> 00:22:50,100
A little to the right.

492
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:51,780
- Like this?
- A bit more to the right.

493
00:22:51,780 --> 00:22:53,140
- There, that should be good.
- Good.

494
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,020
- Good, good.
- Alright.

495
00:22:54,020 --> 00:22:54,820
Hand it to me.

496
00:23:00,700 --> 00:23:01,860
Wasn't it just here?

497
00:23:01,860 --> 00:23:02,700
This spot.

498
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:03,740
The frame is here this way.

499
00:23:08,620 --> 00:23:09,380
You got it?

500
00:23:09,620 --> 00:23:10,380
Yes.

501
00:23:12,060 --> 00:23:12,980
Forget it. Give it to me.

502
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:14,780
You can't even hammer a nail in.

503
00:23:14,780 --> 00:23:16,380
Who says I can't?

504
00:23:16,380 --> 00:23:17,140
Let me do it.

505
00:23:20,980 --> 00:23:22,140
Your drawing

506
00:23:22,500 --> 00:23:23,380
is pretty good.

507
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:25,620
You're quite talented.

508
00:23:26,340 --> 00:23:27,500
Don't praise me all of a sudden.

509
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:28,500
I'm not used to it.

510
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:30,620
You're not used to compliments?

511
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:33,660
What's wrong? Is your hand okay?

512
00:23:33,660 --> 00:23:34,540
It's fine.

513
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:35,780
You surprised me with the compliment,

514
00:23:35,780 --> 00:23:36,780
